# fs.nvfs.api — arena_* trait alias.
#
# Decision (recorded here per Phase 5 brief): the `Arena` trait is owned
# by `std.storage.arena` because spostgre and other storage consumers need
# the SAME trait without importing the whole `fs/nvfs/` module. This file
# therefore re-exports via a `use` so NVFS callers can write
# `use std.fs.nvfs.api.{Arena, ArenaHandle, ArenaAppendResult}` while the
# underlying definition stays in one place.
#
# Source: doc/05_design/nvfs_design.md §4, doc/05_design/spostgre_design.md §11.

use std.storage.arena.{Arena, ArenaHandle, ArenaAppendResult}
